KeysToEntries.story_3_4_000:
Back from Akina
and this is waiting for me…
KeysToEntries.story_3_4_001:
Damn it…
what the hell’s going on
here…?
KeysToEntries.story_3_4_002:
I chewed out some
spineless punk,
so I’m still wound up.
KeysToEntries.story_3_4_003:
The RedSuns don’t usually
battle on home turf…
KeysToEntries.story_3_4_004:
Get over here…
stand at the start.
KeysToEntries.story_3_4_005:
I’ll wipe you out
just to let off steam.
